

=Bio=

Sociologist and director of the Stiftungsgemeinschaft anstiftung & ertomis. She researches and publishes about sustainable lifestyles, urban gardening and sustainable concepts of welfare. She is editor of "[[edited::Urban Gardening]]" (2011) and co-author of "[[authored::Stadt der Commonisten]]" (2013).


